{"tid":572050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【戥你開心】秃毛成身生蚤仲盲眼 ，小狗獲救唔同晒！","createTime":"2018-02-25T08:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T12:54:53.000Z","uid":29314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0cf0bbca9a33aec90c62c0a8f59e975b7b30b95d","tid":572050,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T08:49:07.000Z","msg":"流浪狗「Frodo」去年5月在街上被熱心人士希貢亞克（Klaudija Sigunjak）救起，當時牠因患有狗蚤、獸疥癬及牛蜱（tick），毛髮粗硬又稀少，細菌感染亦導致牠的眼球凸出。希貢亞克憶述時指：「我被嚇呆了，我難以相信那是一隻狗。」他不忍牠繼續流浪街頭，用食物贏得「Frodo」信任，令牠重新習慣與人類為伴。<br />\n<br />\n小狗其後獲安排領養，新主人對牠愛護有加，帶牠接受獸醫治療。雖然牠的右邊眼球因受嚴重感染需要移除，但牠經治療後皮膚病已痊癒，毛髮亦重新健康生長。「世上最醜狗狗」猶如重獲新生，連最初救起牠的希貢亞克也稱：「我們從沒想過牠會變得如此漂亮。」"},{"pid":"922c10479a5baa687c098a2fb1c7284a9b093537","tid":572050,"uid":29314,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T08:49:51.000Z","msg":"之前：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180223/large/1519370023_40b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180223%2Flarge%2F1519370023_40b8.jpg&h=1795921c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6f57ae85fddc51a3dceb4cbf7611dcf35559bf1","tid":572050,"uid":29314,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T08:50:37.000Z","msg":"之後：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180223/large/1519370027_b33c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180223%2Flarge%2F1519370027_b33c.jpg&h=c175ee4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180223/large/1519370032_3fc6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180223%2Flarge%2F1519370032_3fc6.jpg&h=c8cc4f12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"94f46bcd98d3276ecb6a42c4393403b271a1d9e4","tid":572050,"uid":760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T08:51:42.000Z","msg":"Nice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd2c504b4a8914bcf596ab7b8ff49bb6c9f74105","tid":572050,"uid":20750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T08:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好靚仔"},{"pid":"53d61c38ec4655f6e2cb6ecfe4366e2feec65c01","tid":572050,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T10:50:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇到都開心"},{"pid":"1ebba992e59c23b5d7ce472985c80c847b4055ee","tid":572050,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T12:54:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}